doctype html
html
  head
    title Sandberg–Sessions Wedding
    = javascript_include_tag "//use.typekit.net/kdj8ujz.js"
    javascript:
      try{Typekit.load();}catch(e){}
    = stylesheet_link_tag "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Pacifico", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true
    = stylesheet_link_tag    'static', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true
    = javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true
    = csrf_meta_tags
    meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1"
  body
    .landing
      .band.lightblue
        .container
          header#title
            hgroup.cursive
              h1 Jeff & Stephanie
              h2 are getting married!
            hgroup.serif
              = time_tag Date.new(2014,07,12)
              p San Francisco, California
      .band.darkblue
        .container
          .ceremony
            .icon
            hgroup.serif
              h1 Ceremony
              em 2 PM
              h2
                a href="https://www.google.com/maps/preview#!q=Pulgas+Water+Temple&data=!1m4!1m3!1d12844!2d-122.3292264!3d37.4916603!4m15!2m14!1m13!1s0x0%3A0x35aaf9caca753a32!3m8!1m3!1d12844!2d-122.3292264!3d37.4916603!3m2!1i1440!2i779!4f13.1!4m2!3d37.4833211!4d-122.3171103" target="blank" Pulgas Water Temple
            p.serif
              | Our wedding ceremony is at the beautiful #{link_to "Pulgas Water Temple, on Cañada Road", "https://www.google.com/maps/preview#!q=Pulgas+Water+Temple&data=!1m4!1m3!1d12844!2d-122.3292264!3d37.4916603!4m15!2m14!1m13!1s0x0%3A0x35aaf9caca753a32!3m8!1m3!1d12844!2d-122.3292264!3d37.4916603!3m2!1i1440!2i779!4f13.1!4m2!3d37.4833211!4d-122.3171103"}
          .reception
            .icon
            hgroup.serif
              h1 Reception
              em 3:30 PM
              h2
                a href="https://www.google.com/maps/preview#!q=Crystal+Springs+United+Methodist+Church%2C+Bunker+Hill+Drive%2C+San+Mateo%2C+CA&data=!4m15!2m14!1m13!1s0x808f9fcef68a814d%3A0xe969da962dec1ca4!3m8!1m3!1d12846!2d-122.3084281!3d37.4822485!3m2!1i1440!2i779!4f13.1!4m2!3d37.522215!4d-122.341754" Crystal Springs Church
            p.serif
              | We will be hosting a small reception in the social hall of #{link_to "Crystal Springs Methodist Church", "https://www.google.com/maps/preview#!q=Crystal+Springs+United+Methodist+Church%2C+Bunker+Hill+Drive%2C+San+Mateo%2C+CA&data=!4m15!2m14!1m13!1s0x808f9fcef68a814d%3A0xe969da962dec1ca4!3m8!1m3!1d12846!2d-122.3084281!3d37.4822485!3m2!1i1440!2i779!4f13.1!4m2!3d37.522215!4d-122.341754"}
      .band.white
        .container
          .groom
            hgroup
              h1 The Groom
              h2 Jeff Sandberg
            p
              | Jeff is the son of two geeks, and is a geek himself. He grew up in Los Alamos, NM and moved to Kennewick, WA when he was 12. During his formative middle and high school years his hobbies were playing video games with friends, surfing the web, and skiing.
            p
              | After high school, Jeff attended the University of Utah in Salt Lake City. He landed his first job at reddit as an undergraduate, then afterwards worked elsewhere as a ruby on rails programmer. He currently works for OneLogin, and lives in the Rincon Hill neighborhood of San Francisco.
          .bride
            hgroup
              h1 The Bride
              h2 Stephanie Sessions
