      .band.lightblue.story
        .container
          h1.cursive Our Story
          section
            p
              | The bride and groom first met in middle school music class. They got to know each other through band trips, events, and shared classes.
            p
              | After graduating from high school, both moved to Salt Lake City. Stephanie enrolled at the LDS Business College while Jeff enrolled in the University of Utah. Both being new students in a new city with a common past, they began spending more time together. Their first date was simple, a trip to a Subway to get dinner. From that point, their relationship grew.
            p
              | A few years later, Jeff proposed to Stephanie!
